# titleize

> Capitalize every word in a string: `unicorn cake` → `Unicorn Cake`

## Install

```
$ npm install titleize
```

## Usage

```js
import titleize from 'titleize';

titleize('foo bar');
//=> 'Foo Bar'

titleize('foo-bar');
//=> 'Foo-Bar'
```

